Title: The Stonewall riot
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3csypyq
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 1 Jul 2019
The riot that inspired the modern gay rights movement; Saddam Hussein's 1980s genocidal campaign against Iraq's Kurds; notorious British serial killers, Fred and Rose West; 50 years of fighting for fat people in America; and Joseph Heller on his seminal work, Catch-22. Picture: the Stonewall Inn today (Getty Images) Show less